description: Isis took the next step in becoming a US superstar. Practicing and taking lessons on her own time, she came into season two ready. Her first Victim is the Vixen. Isis dominates her in every way, and teaches the Vixen a hard lesson. Girls come here to fight, and sure enough, Vixen got her ass handed to her. Congratulations to Isis on the first win of the new season.
title: WELCOME TO SEASON TWO! Isis (0-0) vs. The Vixen (0-0)
